'       b. Analyze own public board to find ships
'       c. Pick adjacent cell to found ship (hunt mode)
'       d. If no ships found, pick random cell (search mode)
'       e. Execute bomb
'       f. If hit, notify target player
'end

== Game Restart (AI Restore) ==

alt Bot/Server Restart
    AI -> DB: get_all_players() where role=AI
    AI -> DB: get_all_events()
    AI -> GS: GameState.from_events(events)
    note right: AI state restored from\ndatabase + events
end

@enduml
